  "inter_chunk_silence_ms": 650,
  "chunks": [
    {
      "index": 0,
      "text": "On March 31st, Anthropic accidentally published the entire source code for Claude Code.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c1c08fa235b5f0e7dcd51f2fd0520c61d17162a2b5f33ea0cb4249f713316f02",
      "wav": "chunk-00.wav",
      "duration": 5.061950113378685,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 0
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "text": "No hack. No breach. One missing line in a config file did it.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a8c14141ebdba4c710e18c04c234d032156285f3bac7616769573bf73477ba4e",
      "wav": "chunk-01.wav",
      "duration": 3.8080725623582765,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 13
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "text": "The leak exposed 513,000 lines of unobfuscated code.",
      "checksum": "sha256:8f12da69da6568216c4155481192768dbb5493f485093721bf6a71891d1f26d9",
      "wav": "chunk-02.wav",
      "duration": 4.133151927437642,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 26
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "text": "Within hours, the internet downloaded, mirrored, and forked it over 41,000 times.",
      "checksum": "sha256:250962da63ef2fdda0a0b00a126dc9bc54ed12e801d5725ab9414dd0679bedcf",
      "wav": "chunk-03.wav",
      "duration": 4.96907029478458,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 34
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "text": "You cannot unleak a number that big. Anthropic fired off 8,100 DMCA takedowns, then quietly retracted most of them.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f701aa4cdf824575242fc6aea805c01b8ff6fc974a3faa7405323abdad452c87",
      "wav": "chunk-04.wav",
      "duration": 7.291065759637188,
      "word_count": 19,
      "words_offset": 46
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "text": "Meanwhile, a developer in Korea built Claw-Code.",
      "checksum": "sha256:25ef17cb93fa2fe07afc13358f0c1e115bdf04c8d75516ffadb8bf8e058009da",
      "wav": "chunk-05.wav",
      "duration": 3.01859410430839,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 65
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "text": "A clean-room Python clone. It hit 75,000 stars in 2 hours.",
      "checksum": "sha256:73ba751b72b815ccc97a3ffbdb0a711ad7c4afc565b697eab9ddfa5d9cc00fe9",
      "wav": "chunk-06.wav",
      "duration": 3.8545124716553287,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 72
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "text": "Possibly the fastest growing repo in GitHub history.",
      "checksum": "sha256:465a7a427ac95bc95d34a4a47adbbad76776229dbe62ec93fe2aa93c1c9c26e6",
      "wav": "chunk-07.wav",
      "duration": 2.8328344671201813,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 83
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "text": "Here is the twist. Anthropic says Claude Code is 90 percent written by Claude itself.",
      "checksum": "sha256:6d1feece2904179ac6a6c23afc882b103efd1db4ca991bd114fcb88a8a64b988",
      "wav": "chunk-08.wav",
      "duration": 4.922630385487528,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 91
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "text": "And U.S. courts have ruled AI-generated work gets no copyright protection.",
      "checksum": "sha256:0fd4d4a5a81216ad432c5d69ffb06173d0a1e4963c506bdb07f246b38534a82e",
      "wav": "chunk-09.wav",
      "duration": 4.31891156462585,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 106
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "text": "So who actually owns the code they are fighting to take down?",
      "checksum": "sha256:b9b33445d8ade55d1d8b8d4547973691ecd71046089ec4c867c478afe3852fc9",
      "wav": "chunk-10.wav",
      "duration": 3.1579138321995464,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 117
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "text": "Drop your answer below. A lot of you asked how I learn this AI stuff.",
      "checksum": "sha256:8dd18a736f127c3320772e15be857f28c93a8d8ca490cb713524ede33c7830c9",
      "wav": "chunk-11.wav",
      "duration": 4.365351473922902,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 129
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "text": "I'm on the Dynamous team. I work with Cole on workshops, his videos, and our open source projects.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9b4274225fe70611ad9375cca53159026b6cf79076944bf6386be328741a7f96",
      "wav": "chunk-12.wav",
      "duration": 5.38702947845805,
      "word_count": 18,
      "words_offset": 144
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "text": "There's a 10% off code in the pinned comment if you want to join us.",
      "checksum": "sha256:98876ad6d51bc2e3dfe6cdba070fe9d3d570ff8cd4256c105e627da3b967055a",
      "wav": "chunk-13.wav",
      "duration": 3.4829931972789114,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 162
    }
  ]
}